c: 35
v: 8
t: "Kodi iye,amene zoipa zake zimaoneka ngati zabwino, moti akamaziona amati ndi zabwino? Ndithudi Mulungu amasocheretsa aliyense amene amamufuna ndiponso amatsogolera aliyense amene wamufuna. Kotero usavutike mu mtima mwako chifukwa cha iwo. Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene amachita"